result.name: Fire N Ice

reviews.text: They serve a great variety of cocktails (Whiskey cocktails are a MUST TRY). The place has got an electrifying ambience and an awesome DJ which makes it a great place for anyone who wants to groove to some good music. MUST VISIT.
Amazing restaurant, Food and service was top notch when i visited with family. Great recommendation for everyone. We were thrilled to have tried this place.
The right place to start and finish your night right. Different versions of music from time to time. The atmosphere is well lit with events going across the calendar. A big shout!

It can definitely be your to-go spot!
Ask the bar tender for whiskey cocktails and mention your taste preference and they’d surprise you really well! 
保持
One of the most happening place!! Def. worth a visit if you are visiting the town! Cheers🥂
